title: Do Da Dancin'!: Venice Kokusai-hen
original_name: Do Da Dancin'! ヴェネチア国際編
sinopse:
Sakuraba Taiko is now 25 years old, and is aiming to win the International Ballet Contest in Venice! A new challenge starts for Taiko and her love for ballet. The long-awaited next chapter in this passionate dancing story!

(Source: Amazon)
